        "timestamp": "2019-04-06 23:15:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI'm not sure what the procedure would be if we have already deployed ONAP without security enabled but now want to enable it. Would it be to edit the properties in the file ./oom/kubernetes/dmaap/components/dmaap-bc/resources/config/dmaapbc.properties and then redeploy dev-dmaap by first helm delete, then cleanup.sh, make dev-dmaap, make onap, helm deploy dev-dmaap?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
