        "timestamp": "2019-04-08 06:28:39.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDefault setting for security is now: true. Enable/disable is just change the useAAF in properties (DataSet of Kubernetes) and restart/recreate pod.",
        "patchset_number": 1
